  "detailed_description": "Cursed House 5 is a game in the Match 3 puzzle genre, where levels are completed in a specific sequence of actions.<br />\r\nFor the first time in this series, Cursed House introduces a bonus system that will remain with minimal changes in several upcoming projects.<br />\r\nThe game includes:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n90 Match 3 levels<br />\r\n10 Hidden Object scenes<br />\r\n10 Spot the Difference scenes<br />\r\n20 Solitaire games<br />\r\nA beautiful old mansion that needs to be restored and cleansed of evil spirits",
